cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.GT, cs.CV. 

The paper presents a novel reinforcement learning algorithm that combines planning policies and generalization of those plans, which is relevant to several sub-fields of computer science. The use of deep neural networks for generalization suggests that the paper could belong to cs.AI and cs.LG. The application of the algorithm to robotic control and game playing suggests that it could belong to cs.RO and cs.GT. Finally, the mention of board game Hex suggests that the paper could also belong to cs.CV, as computer vision techniques are often used in analyzing board games.
